      <p class="text-lg text-pink-400 mb-8">
        Professional, loving care for your furry family members. We treat every
        dog like our own, giving you peace of mind while you're away.
      </p>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row space-y-4 sm:space-y-0 sm:space-x-4"
      >
        <a
          href="#contact"
          class="bg-pink-200 hover:bg-purple-700 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg text-center shadow-lg transform hover:scale-105 transition duration-300"
          >Contact Us</a
